			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/BGO_Main_A\r\n- Go to Carmen's cosmetics shop ( S_WYR_FigaroSister_DEBUG_Point_5d7b1276-f516-49f2-b3ea-3564b25cd35c ) and enter to make Naaber follow you.\r\n- Lead him outside, somewhere unseen, and Ctrl+Shift+K kill him.\r\n- \"addDebugSpell Target_SpeakWithDead_Test\"\r\n- Cast the SwD spell on him."
				},
